model = DistMult(batches_count=2, seed=555, epochs=1, k=10, loss='pairwise',
    loss_params={'margin': 5}, optimizer='adagrad', optimizer_params={'lr':
    0.1})
X = np.array([['a', 'y', 'b'], ['b', 'y', 'a'], ['a', 'y', 'c'], ['c', 'z',
    'a'], ['a', 'z', 'd']])
model.fit(X)
X1 = np.array([['a', 'y', 'b'], ['b', 'y', 'a'], ['a', 'y', 'c'], ['c', 'z',
    'a'], ['g', 'z', 'd']])
X2 = np.array([['a', 'y', 'b'], ['b', 'y', 'a'], ['a', 'y', 'c'], ['c', 'z',
    'a'], ['a', 'x', 'd']])
assert model.is_fitted_on(X) is True
assert model.is_fitted_on(X1) is False
assert model.is_fitted_on(X2) is False
